_header: Jesu that art of might most / Father and son and holy ghost
_description: Reinbrun Gy Sone of Warwike — 127 12-line stanzas (aabaabccbddb)

NLS1921.First Lines:
Ihesu þat ert of miȝte mostfader & sone & holy
                    gost…
NLS1921.Last Lines:
…þai toke lone an hiȝeIn to ingelonde þai gonne
                    saile…
NLS1921.Note: Ends imperfectly due to lost leaf or leaves.
